comments: ["This is app is completely incontainable, the greediness of this app, It's like your craving money. At least one thing couldn't be a free trial, I mean come on! How could one be so selfish, I've also went through the app. Anybody who gets this app make sure to look at the ratings everytime you download something. Remove the app because I don't know if your scams are able to be allowed on this media.", "While frankly, it doesn't really work, the gimmick is fun to play with your pups. But a heads up to everyone, there is no 3 day free trial. They charged me right after the 24 hour mark of installing the app on the trial. So heads up,nuse it for an hour and delete it.", 'App was good when I saw it, I thought "Oh, maybe I can tell my dog what not to do since showing is working but not he\'s not paying attention, but as soon as I was about to use the recording it asks me for money, terrible app and I barely opened the app too', 'Scam, tried to use the 3 day trial but the app insisted on charging me today hence no 3 day free trial, total scam proving that moving forward would only lead to stupidity of actually purchasing the app', 'Lost a customer due to their greedy concept... I downloaded this and had a little play about however the ads for premium were too full on They offer a 3-day "FREE" Trial yet charge the money in ADVANCE?!..... that\'s not how it should work as they should well know...... Had I been able to use the 3 Day free trial I possibly would have purchased this however I refuse to pay for a product that I have not been able to try as it states.....', "Up front subscription and you don't even get to test it without putting in your billing information. $20 a year too? Get outta here.", 'DON\'T DO THE 3 DAY "FREE" TRIAL! it will instantly charge you the 30 dollars and I looked at the charged dates for it and there is nothing about a free trial. It instantly charged me and says it will charge me again one year from now not even one year and three days. I emailed to see if I could get a refund, waiting for a reply. False advertising 100%', 'Too many ads. Every time you mess around with the app, after EVERY dog call, there is an ad. And on top of that, you have to buy a subscription for either $10 a month or $100 a year for an app that should cost $5 to have forever. To just not have ads playing after every press of a button. Garbage app that paid for its rating.', "I was charged double for a trial for the $10 monthly payment. It was for testing purposes to see if the app works and was bought today and never went to next month to write a review saying that I was double charged. I would say that for me it sort of worked and the others not sure because most of my dogs are lazy. App is professional looking when being on the app for like fifteen minutes, I've never had an ad yet for the fifteen minutes I've been on. Otherwise, the trial was like not a trial.", "Rubbish. After pressing 3 things in the app it was just constant ad popups and membership requests, entire ap became unusable. Its absolutely ridiculous, app is just supposed to be a bit of fun, don't really know if it's actually any good usability wise because I didn't get a chance to find out. If it was then yeah, I'd probably pay a couple quid in the app store for it but they block of the whole app and want £25 per year for use. You'd have to be insane.", "Do not install. I agreed to the free trail (because you have to, to continue to the app and try it out). I tried it out for 5 minutes and realised all the barks are the same and it is just all lies. Anyway, I cancelled the trail so I won't be charged after it. Lone behold, I check my bank the next say and they've already charged me for a month. Just don't waste your time on this app. Its not often I leave reviews but after this experience I can imagine that's how they make their money.", 'DO NOT USE THIS APP!! I downloaded this app. and I chose the 3-day free trial/1 month. The app said it will not charge me until after the trial period ended. The app does not do what it claims, so I canceled within 10 minutes of downloading the app. They had already charged my account. (Stole my money) They gave me a hard time when I asked for a refund. I had to get my credit card company involved along with Google.', '"Free trial" doesn\'t exist and is false advertising. The app is designed poorly and even with the pay version, you are still forced to watch ads. Developer doesn\'t respond to inquiries. Fail on so many levels. Super disappointing.', 'When I looked at the reviews, it said that it was nice, good and that kind of stuff. So I decided to download this app so I could understand my dog, and at first it was going well for me. After some few minutes when playing it it kept asking me to buy premium or whatever that was.Like after I pressed some specific buttons in this app it would always tell me to buy that premium thing.Dont really know but if you would want to advertise your app adding too many premium ads wont really end up well.', "Literally the worst app I've ever downloaded. To be honest it was just a waste of time. I tried using the dog translator to talk to my dog but using it would cost 25$ MONTHLY such a wase of money! The only TWO free things I could use wouldn't work because every time I tapped it it wouldn't do anything. This app sucks and DONT DOWNLOAD IT!! It's a waste of storage.", 'Not free. It even says that you can get a 3 day free trial but it charges $30 per year after 3 days. However, when you get to the Google play page to start the "trial," it says that the $30 starts today. They obviously use this money to pay for fake good reviews. Deceptive and misleading. Do not get this one.', "This is filled with TONS of ads. You have to watch a 30 second video to unlock EACH bark, and then you have to watch a ~6 second video to use the same bark thereafter. The audio of the videos are pretty loud, and the dog barks aren't as loud, and the barks play *immediately* when the ad is finished. It almost sounds like the ad ends with a faint dog bark. It gives no time between the bark and the ad to distinguish the bark as being by itself. Be better to have fewer barks and no ads.", 'It works perfectly. Especially with premium!!! I love it!! Make and app that translates dog into human language please!!! I highly recommend this app. Works so well my dogs are learning tricks now, very efficiently. This app unlike many others actually works many Dogify apps we have used haven’t worked. We quickly saw great improvements great improvements when we would make when we would use the sit noise they would sit it works great. Love this app so so much!!!!! If you are having trouble with dog training get this app! If you just want to talk to them use it to!!!!!...', "This is the worst app! Had to watch 6 ads just as i opened it. Every click and there's a 30 second ad you can't skip, don't waste your time and energy!", 'EDITED: The cost of free trial has been refunded. 1-star is edited to 4-star since the app does not work well to my dogs. PREVIOUS; The 3 day free trial is actually a one year charge. Feel like a scam to me. The price is not worth it for about $20. Not works for my dogs. But they seem to react like they heard something.', "I WASNT ABLE TO PLAY WITHOUT PAYINGG!would not recommend this game if you don't Like to pay MONEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!SO if you don't like spending money and you like saving money i would not recommend dis game cuz you have to pay for EVERYTHINGGG SO if you want to pay them go ahead but I would rather not play it cuz it probaly cost 250$ for everything in total but if your paying only 1 thing it cost 2 things and yeah I don't like to spend money and pls make a free version Thank You Very Muchhhhh <3", "I have no idea why I downloaded this it's useless you press any button it automatically switches screens to you must pay $30 to use app are you out of your flipping mind you stupid idiots who in their right mind is going to spend $30 on an app that does not work. If you ask a question of would I refer this app to a friend I would rather jump off the Earth face first into a pile of dog poop", "I was charged a full year subscription when I tried for a free trial. And even after that, the app still doesn't work. It still shows that I need to pay before using the translator. Please, just return my money.", "A waste. There's no helpful info under training. Cancelled subscription same day during trial period and was still charged. Developer does not respond. Google won't refund. So it's just a loss. Don't waste your money.", 'who knew once you downloaded this app and hit the microphone, that it was a subscription app that cost money.....lame.', "$20 for a gag app. and you can't even mess with it without paying. stupid. don't waste your time", "Firstly, 3 days trial period was not there as mentioned, amount got deducted immediately. Secondly, even after amount being deducted for subscription, the app still doesn't allow us to use its features, the subscription page keeps popping up.", "They let you try like 3 sounds then from that point on you have to pay $30 for the premium version so it's just a big scam basically. Don't bother downloading it.", "I have paid for subscription but I cannot access at all. Google subscription says I have to open the app to confirm plan but everytime I do, there's no button to confirm the plan. Totally wasted money for nothing. I wish you will refund", "Offers 3 day trial with offer to cancel without being charged. It immediately charges your card. Despite canceling the same day, I am stuck with the charge and an app that doesn't work.", 'DO NOT download this app!!! They offer a 3 day free trial but I cancelled the subscription trial 10 minutes after trying it and uninstalled the stupid app and they still charged me $35. Stupid as hell.', "Scam app. I downloaded as a joke to see my dogs reaction. They're running a fake 3 day trial. After signing up for the trial with intention to cancel same day... I look and see they plan to charge my card on the day I signed up. Google needs to delete this app from the store. It's quite previously fake... but this is literally illegal false advertising", "Don't download you'll have to buy premium, which offers a free trial but you have to pay in advance, there's tons of better options.", "Martin nimmi. You don't need any of that clickers treats or anything but to snap your fingers give command. Snap and gesture and verbal command. Make it fun talk to him like they're a person. And once they start to understand the command hand gesture and the snapping. Start giving the command word is slightly different a different tone it's like different gesture of your body language. Formulas two parts love one part discipline. Explain everything to them never raise your hand to him That's it.", "I don't know how this app is getting high reviews. I can't even use it, every time I try to do something there's a pop up trying to get you to pay for a subscription and when you close that out and add pops up and then it does it all over again", "Downloaded for the free trial to see how it worked, it's not great, and ended up being charged the full yearly premium despite cancelling almost immediately and the subscription stating trial.", 'Good concept just annoyed that it states a 3 day free trial before subscription but yet you have to upright pay for a subscription without the trial, like how do I know this will work without a trial and wasting $30', "I have a Rottweiler & he didn't understand the language whatever this app has. But the 2star is specifically cause I have been cheated. I subsribed with 3days trial & since the app was not working, I unsubscribed as well as uninstall the app. But still they deducted the amount after 3days. I mean that should not be done.. How come you can deduct an amount whrn I have unsubscribed your service within the trial period? Such a fraud.. Immediately refund the amount.", 'This app completely amazed me! Not only does it work on my dog but on my cat too ! It has tons of sounds to use and the whistle hertz are just on point. My favorite is the squeaky toy and the whistle. I recommend downloading this for not only training, but for some pretty funny sounds.', 'you have to buy the app after you download it to use the functions']

title: Hundeo: Puppy & Dog Training
description:
🐶 Dog & Puppy Training Made Easy 🐕
Don't have a dog trainer or puppy training school with you right now? No problem! Hundeo offers you step-by-step video instructions on the most important topics that a digital dog obedience school can offer you in your pocket. We guide you from puppy to senior with the right content.

300+ Tricks, Games, Recipes and Courses.
Discover a wide range of tricks, games, and recipes for dogs. Get inspiration for your next training session and have fun together. In this app, you can find for example these course topics: Basic Commands, Puppy Basics (Walking the Pup, Potty House Training, Bite inhibition, Puppy Nutrition, Puppy Games, Puppy Commands), Leash Training, Recall Masterclass, How to ignore other dogs on walks, How to behave during a visit, Clicker Course, Dog Impulse control Guide, Health Check at Home, Raw Food Diet, Muzzle Trainer, Calm at Office, New Year's Eve Training, Stop your dog from eating random things, Stop Barking Trainer or Stay Alone Course for Dogs.

Step by Step to Your Goal
We guide you to your goal with our interactive video tutorials.
The tutorials are designed so that you can be successful with just 5 minutes of training a day. It reminds you of your training and when you train successfully, you get a great trophy for your virtual trophy case. In addition to dog training methods, you will also find great activities in the form of pet games and recipes.

Anytime, Anywhere - At Your Own Pace
Out in the park or garden with no reception? No problem. You can download content and use it offline.

New Daily
Daily free quizzes, tricks, games, recipes and courses carefully selected for you. Tailored to you and your breed. (We have 285 dog breeds like Labrador, French Bulldog, Pug, Doberman, Chihuahua)

Playfully to Success
To keep you motivated, you get new challenges every day and earn flames and trophies. 

Individual Profile
Create a profile for your puppy, dog, or even multiple pets and keep track of what you have accomplished and what you still need to practice.

Connect With Others
Have you learned some cool dog or puppy tricks and want to compare yourself with others? Invite your friends or other members of our community to compare your achievements and watch videos of other dogs and puppies.

Your Favorites
Keep track and create your own favorites list for easy access.

Clicker and Whistle Always With You
With a clicker, you always have the right tone with you. A clicker is the most efficient way to teach your puppy tricks and exercises.

Trusted
This app was developed in collaboration with professional dog experts and pet trainers. You can be sure that the exercises will really help you.

Support
If you have any questions about Hundeo or your account, please contact our customer support: support@hundeo.com

Hundeo Plus Membership
To unlock all the features, you can upgrade to ‘hundeo Plus’ and choose between the following subscriptions:
1 month
1 year

Terms and Conditions: https://www.hundeo.com/en/toc/
Privacy policy: https://www.hundeo.com/en/contact/data-protection/

comments: ["The app is pretty good and easy to work around. My only problem is that I have to be on a subscription or premium plan in order to access most of the stuff. People who go to apps for dog training don't really have the money, so they're not going to be able to go on to the premium plan to get access to most of the app. Other than that, it's a good app", "For weeks under maintenance, no training plans available Update: I was not using an old version but I have Adguard on my phone. Seems like the app does not work if it's routed through Adguard...", "I honestly enjoy this training tips it's extremely helpful to me .", 'easy to follow! works well', 'This looks like a really cool app, and I was very excited to use it with my twin cavapoo puppies. But I was dismayed that after I created an account it said that there were only 7 days of a free trial and then I would have to pay for the app and would be automatically billed for it. Beyond not impressed with this bait and switch for what is advertised as a free app. I deleted my account immediately, and I better not be charged in a week.', "I just downloaded & has all the selections of different trainings, tips & tricks. looks like alot of information needed ..HOWEVER, I am needing something to be done QUICK...instead of learning one tip or trick at a time.. it wants to give me ONE lesson one day at a time...I have a dog with separation anxiety & will not stop barking.. barks all night & throughout the day at times.PLEAAE HELP.... I'm still trying other apps as well for the dog barking..whistling apps etc.. I can't afford the prem", 'fun and easy!', "Good app but my dog won't listen to me when I teach her high-five she only listen to me when it's paw or games,☹️", 'Epic I just downloaded I tryed to get her to lie down but she just looked down but well work on it.', "Not Free at all!!! Advertised as free but the only 'free' part is an introduction to each lesson, the introduction only tells you what you will get out of that lesson and gives no advice at all. Don't waste your time unless you want to pay.", 'I tried it with my dog and definitely got results, the tricks and games are great fun for my doggy and honestly cheap for a year of home-training!', 'I love the great video collection. It is also good that there are not only educational videos but also about dog health.', 'Simple, easy to follow tips and tutorials. Helped me finally to get my puppy to sit and control those impulses!', "so far the app is very helpful, Roxie has already picked up on 2 new tricks! She's such a smart little girl!", 'Good free version', 'Very good and helpful I have a young dog and have long been looking for a solution that helps. I really like the step-by-step video tutorials.', 'wow it taught my dog to stay when I went some where yet he has separation anxiety wow thanks', 'it really helped me trane my dog not that good, but it is not the app it is the dog🥰', 'Amazing app should use for sure only thing you need to pay it would be amazimg to gave it for free for some people it would be really useful', "my dog is a puppy and she doesn't now any tricks so I need help", 'tried free version for 7 days, forgot about it and they charged me not even month but for 1 year. Looks like scum.', 'Great for teach dogs tricks,and great recipes so over all brilliant app(my fav trick was little heart♡♡)', "Very nice app but one thing I don't like that is there is not Indian spitz bread option.I hope you will add it.", "DO NOT DOWNLOAD. title: Hello Tiger: Dating App & Chat
description:
Say goodbye to endless swiping, fake profile pictures and pointless messaging, and HELLO to real people, in real time, for FREE.

Hello Tiger is a revolutionary new video dating app which is faster, safer and hassle-free.

Faster
Cut to the chase with one-minute conversations. Why swipe right or left on pictures when you can speed up the whole process and see the real person from the start? Hello Tiger gets you face-to-face to work out if there’s something there or not.

Safer
Putting the control back into your hands. With Hello Tiger, there’s nowhere to hide, what you see is what you get, you can only register with a verified mobile number, and with our strict report and blocking policies you can feel supported every step of the way.

Hassle-free
Tired of the ‘Hey, how was your day?’ and endless bad jokes from people you haven’t even met? Hello Tiger lets you lose the admin and get right down to it. Is there a connection or not? You decide, in under a minute.

_________________

HOW IT WORKS

1. Download the app – it’s completely free; no catch, no in-app purchases or subscriptions.

2. Complete a simple set up – name, age, location, that sort of thing. None of this ‘name your favourite holiday destination’ stuff and no need to write a profile.

3. Add in some criteria for what you’re looking for, so that your matches are exactly what you want, where you want.

4. Before you start, you will need to take a quick picture of yourself and update it weekly – to keep things real. Others will be able to see this photo before they enter into a chat with you, and vice versa – we don’t want there to be any surprises, such as awkward chats with the ex.

5. Now you’re ready to GO LIVE and date. You can either browse your latest matches and click to be notified when someone you like is online, or GO LIVE with online users right away. If someone is online you’d like to get to know a little better, you can move to a live one-minute chat with them, providing they reciprocate the match.

6. During this chat, you can decide quickly if you want to extend it or move onto your next match by selecting one of the following options:

Extend: If you both like each other during the initial chat you will move to one with no time limit and you can get to know each other more. You will then appear in each other’s Favourites so you can message or call each other again, all for free.

Not For Me: Not vibing? That’s ok, better to know now as opposed to meeting in person, right? Simply decline them during the first one-minute chat and you won’t cross paths with them again.

Skip For Now: If you are unsure about the person you’re chatting with, or perhaps didn’t get enough time, you can skip them for now and you may cross paths again later on in the app.

Your personal data is securely stored on Hello Tiger. Be sure to read our terms and conditions, privacy policy and playing safe pages to learn more about the app and how best to use it. 

https://hellotiger.io/tc/

https://hellotiger.io/privacy-policy/

https://hellotiger.io/playing-safe/

comments: ["NZ user here. Looking forward to using this dating app, just can't get past phone number verification, the text with the number never comes through. I tried the resend option numerous times. I did change the country code before attempting verification. Any help please?", 'Can\'t get any email address to register an account, keeps saying "email is not valid", but looks promising. Hopefully the admins or mods will fix this up. (UPDATE: this is outrageous. I have to create a new email address because my existing main email is labelled as "abuse" due to having spam? I\'m sure abuse emails are commonplace and this illegibility does not justify this app\'s poor demands and unnecessary requirements, because of this, this app is not worth more than 1 star, disappointing)', 'Reminds me of Omegle, in a good way. Saw an ad on a bus stop in Coorparoo. A cool concept, yet severely lacking in users: within a 20km radius of the Brisbane CBD there\'s only 3 users in the "Browse users" section, one of which hadn\'t been active in 8 months. The weekly selfie is a good idea, although they are poorly cropped (the middle 3rd of the photo), and there\'s no way to view the whole photo. It would be nice to have the option to write a profile, as the premade options are very limited.', "It's new so will take time to build users but it's free and takes away all the hassles of the usual dating apps. Fake profile pictures are gone, no catfishing, and no dodgy first dates. Plus no advertising or in-app purchases. Let's get behind it, love a Aussie start up!", 'The app looks really cool. Easy to use, great concept. Now just waiting for some people to get in here..', "Love the concept and fact that the people I'm meeting are who they say they are. A good change to some of the more traditional dating apps I've used...", 'This app does not show any matches in the area and takes too long to load such a waste of time', 'It takes forever just to see people waste of time', 'I does not accept my email', "At last, a dating app that's not for the fake hearted.", "Waiting time just doesn't seem to get over..", "Real women! That's a difference.", 'Great app!']

title: WooPlus - Dating App for Curvy
description:
WooPlus, the largest BBW online dating and chat app, is the cupid for plus-size singles and people who admire curvy singles.

❤️ Best Plus Size & BBW Dating App with 8M+ users, NO fat-shaming.

❤️ Featured on BBC, Forbes, Google Play & the App Store.️

Meet new people & date local plus-size ladies and chubby singles in New York, Los Angeles, Chicago, Las Vegas, San Antonio, Philadelphia, and other US cities, as well as the UK, Canada, Australia, Germany, and other parts of the world!  

Start Dating With:

EASY CHAT - "Say Hi" to your match & start chatting! FUN EXPERIENCE - The video feature shows charm & gets you more matches! REAL PEOPLE - All profiles are professionally checked to block bots and scammers. INCLUSIVE VIBES - Meet new people nearby, meet local curvy singles who love your full-figured body.  

Meet Your Love:

WooPlus is a free dating app for adults and people who like to meet & date curvy girls, super-size big beautiful women (SSBBW), and chubby guys, whether you're black, Latino, Asian, or interracial, or seeking mature dating and LGBTQ relationships (lesbian, gay or bisexual). But if you're just looking for a ONS, FWB, sugar baby seeking sugar daddy for arrangement, casual encounters dating, or threesome affairs, WooPlus may not be the dating site for you.  

Social Buzz:

🌟 “Plus-size dating app WooPlus will now ban ‘fat-shaming fools’” - YAHOO 🌟 “WooPlus, hailed as an answer to Tinder for the bigger and rounder female population.'' - MIRROR   -Connect with us on social: @wooplus_dating (Instagram, TikTok) -Terms of Service: https://www.wooplus.com/terms -Privacy Policy: https://www.wooplus.com/privacy -Dating Tips: https://www.wooplus.com/bbwdating

comments: ["Great app! I've tried a lot of dating apps and this has always been my favorite.... Some people have seen it and they like the design very much. Use is smooth and intuitive. Tired of being combative, they had to swipe every configuration file. With this, you can pass a dozen at the same time, saving a lot of time!.", 'Wooplus is a really good dating app, it performs as advertised, and give much more reasonable options for single parents than other apps. The algorhythm is far more forgiving than other apps, and I find matches much faster than its competitors, the premium is also very affordable. The only downside is that the app does not work on data, at 5G and full bars, the app as no connection or service, which makes forming a connection with someone quite hard within the app.', "I wish I had learned about WooPlus sooner. I had trouble locating people on other apps with whom I actually clicked. They just always seemed to fizzle out in conversation or fail miserably in real life. They just didn't feel right, and they were unable to explain why. I've only just started using this app, but it's clear that the people I'm corresponding with are much more compatible.", "Balanced experience at the moment. I'm trying to update a few things on my profile, and it keeps running an unsuccessful save after I've entered everything. (-1400) Not sure why this is happening as the app has just been updated.", 'This app is horrible! It allows users to list disgusting sexual requests. Yet my profile was deleted due to me letting those interested know what expectations I as for in a potential match. The potential matches are always too far. Very few are in your city. This app is a waste of time. I do not recommend.', 'Garbage app, pretty much everything paywall and the app is not great, looks just okay but no functionality like nowhere to delete messages and most ppl that message you there is no way to block them, that feature only shows for a few.', "I've never had luck with dating apps, but this app has a feature where you can chat with someone and only after a little while talking does it show each person what the other looks like. I gave it a shot on a whim one night. Call it thanks to either dumb luck, fate, or this app, but I met my first ever girlfriend on this app on my first attempt on the FlashChat feature and I'm meeting her family in a few days. I couldn't be happier 😁", 'App is very predatory, will actively search people interstate unless you pay for the "premium" service. Makes tinder look like a good app. Wooplus used to be a half decent app, but now it\'s just a cash grab.', "For the most part it seems like a great app that I'm getting pretty into! However the issue I have is a big one The thing is that it's very unclear of the sexualities of other people. Often I find myself scared to talk to people because I'm not sure if their bi-sexual, gay, straight, etc. Id be happy to give 5 stars, but I just wish some things weren't so vague...", "It's pretty cool, love that you get notifications for almost everything so you're not waiting for days to heat back from someone. I also like that it's very detailed. The only thing I don't like is not being able to see my likes without paying.", 'I can encounter some great matches in many features on this dating app. Those features are really unique and useful. So for those bbw dating finders who yearn for finding some great dating partners, this is our best choice! I like this curvy tinder app, I get what I want here.', "Overall, it's a good app. The only thing I would say is that it would be nice if you could choose the region for free as well as preference, age and distance in fact all preferences. If the messaging was free for basic users, that would also be great. Maybe if the person is VIP , use 💎 just a thought.", "Absolutely useless for me, I've downloaded the app twice now and it won't let me progress any further than adding my phone number so I can't create my account. Going to look for a more user friendly app.", "Awful app. Most of the people on here are bots and scammers. It's also incredibly restrictive and is extremely hard to actually talk to someone. I was offered a deal for 12.99 for three months. I saw that I was charged for the full price instead of the discounted price since I used this service before. However, on the charge screen it doesn't explain that. Sent an email to support and said they wouldn't refund me and hope I understand. Luckily, Google had my back and refunded me.", "Well, I wish I could say I found someone on this app but haven't. You really need to give more swipes. At least 25 or 40 a day. Then unlimited if you do a month payment", 'The app is easy to use havnt matched with any obvious bots but some profiles do just get the X for being sus. Found a few matches but didnt want to keep chatting after first night. As with all dating apps its free to play but pay to win, you gain a significant advantage by whaling, but loging in each day and playing the dating game will slowly have you finding a few people. App started matching me with people across the world weirdly which is undesireable. Wouldnt pay to subscribe personally.', 'The site has plenty of scammers. It is sad that the developers do not take our privacy and safety Seriously. My suggestion is to change by taking appropriate safety measures before allowing anyone located in the world to use the app freely. Applicants should be asked to identify themselves by taking a selfie and sending it to your team to investigate before joining. Such measures are being taken by your competition to keep us safe because they care, and so should you. Thank you kindly.', "While not the best looking app, it is one of the more functional (when you're not swamped by profiles looking to sell their services).", "I have quite a few profiles under 'my likes' that I either passed on or never even viewed, so I am getting a few incorrect matches. Seems a bit pointless for a dating app? I'm now correcting my rating down because I am tired of constantly being shown the same people - people I have swiped past many times just keep coming back again and again and again. What's the point in going through them if you're only ever looking at the same 10 potential matches?", "I dont think there is a single person left on the app, I've used it before with decent success, 80 likes or so. Used it for a week with the paid thing and didn't get a single like", 'May be real accounts but most are for OnlyFans/Snapchat purposes. Free features are horrid. Search is too basic instead of ease of close by. App performs well tho.', "You only get to like 20 people a day. Everyone you talk to on their seems well Out Of Reach. No one lives within 30 miles and no one has tried to talk to me yet. Feels like all the other app only worse. You have to pay to play and then the only way you're really able to make the most of it is to spend extra money even though you've already spent money on a month membership. I wouldn't be surprised if most of profiles were AI.", 'For some reason I never match with the ones that like me. And I never get them recommended as well. So it seems to be the app is broken. Or people outside my preferences can like me. But even then they will not be recommended. Sorry to the 8 people who gave me a like.', "Doesn't tell you that they are going to charge you until you've set an account up, and then you get stuck in a loop screen trying to cancel and the only way to get out of it is to exit the app with task manager. If I could give you less I would.", "I mostly see people from other states. I still run out of matches even though there is no use trying to match with them since they are too far. There isn't a way to set a distance preference either", 'I\'m trying to sign up and it\'s not letting me. It\'s always "internal error 100003" and it\'s annoying. I\'ve tried over 40 times and it\'s saying the same thing. Pls help meee 😭😭', 'Horrible glitches and it keeps going to the same person over and over. I asked for my money back after this poor experience. We will see if it happens. Later: They told me they would refund my money to my Google account. That was 07/14/23 and over 24 hrs ago. Nothing. I am so frustrated with this app. So many fake accounts, too.', 'No one responds and it gives you more matches way outside of where you live no matter what your app settings are. This is not a good site to meet people and is a waste of time and money.', "Do you have to purchase a subscription to get or see that you've gotten likes? I know I'm not everyone's cup of tea, but I have been using this app for about 2 weeks, and I haven't gotten even one like. And most people are too far away. The idea for the app is nice, but it fails in execution.", "Useless. Constant error messages, and when it does work, it's suggesting people 150 miles away.", "This app is WHACK, you have to pay to do anything worthwhile. Why do I have to get VIP access just to see who liked me? And anybody can message you if they're VIP, from anywhere. People you wouldn't even match with. I'm not paying $14.99 a month for something I can do for free elsewhere. I had a better experience using FB dating, at least I can see who likes me. There's also no good explanation on how to use this app either, I'm just clicking stuff to see what's what. Just a mess.", 'Useless app. Can only look at so many profiles a day and they keep showing the same people over and over after clearly not being interested!!', "Woo plus , it's a much better dating app. Than most just full of Fakes from Africa nigeria or Russian & yes I found out from where. And yes 80% Fakers on most dating sites .Most are specially designed to steal money from men all day long. That are lying to you trying to steal your money hidden behind a Beautiful fake pictures. Very few dating sites are clean enough by over 80% non fakes. And that's what this app is way ,way cleaner than most.", "DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY OR TIME 🚩 The profiles are inactive. I paid for the premium subscription and haven't received likes or matches in days, it's practically a ghost town dating app. If anyone does chat with you beware they're most likely a scammer pretending to be in the military and out of the country. 🤨 I want my money back. I basically paid to like fake/inactive profiles. Scam app! 🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩", "Nice app, in theory. Cool spin on dating app features. I like the flash chat and open forum in moments. I'm a free user because I have a problem paying for things I feel should be free. Would've been 4 stars b/c I don't like the most recent promotion or the few matches to likes. I have 70+ likes that I can't see, which is fine b/c free is my favorite. But in my rounds they only send 1 or 2 of them. I think they're in cahoots with scammers b/c they deleted my bio for mentioning scam behaviors", 'Easy to use. You\'re set up in less then 5 minutes. I do wish that the filters you set up extended to the daily picks and who is able to see your profile. Lots of "likes" from men younger or older than my started range. So good but not perfect.', 'Not impressed. Super complex UI with almost everything behind a paywall and I\'m not even entirely sure if I\'ll get a match without paying. It\'s also difficult to set your location. All of the attractive women have tons of comments and likes on their "posts" so it\'s not really worth the effort.', 'I like how it fills the plus size niche very well. Profiles seem genuine. I like the FREE messaging only once mutually liked each other approach. Edit: I subscribed to the premium service, largely to support this, and discovered it\'s now worse! Instead of only messaging after mutual likes, I\'m forced to cold message now... Not worth. Edit2: The "hi" feature is behind a paywall now and the Lucky Draw draws you a discount for paying for Premium. How lucky O.O lowering rating', "Just like all other dating apps just another waste of time. They all claim to be completely free but notice it says #10 grossing app because like the rest they lure you in to pay with fake profiles but you will never find anyone in your area or have to pay to actually talk to someone because the people that message you are bots and you can't really message anyone. Even if it was security reasons it would at least be a feature to let you or a person choose to get a message.", 'I get the monetization of platforms and I understand that the app is free, mostly, but now being charged to send a greeting which you could only send daily for free anyways, now that\'s a bit of an overreach. They took the ability to look at your old matches and monetized it. Now you can\'t even send a simple "Hi".']

title: Bumble: Dating App & Friends
description:
Welcome to Bumble 💛 The community with millions of people where you can find dates, make new friends, and meet people.

Bumble is a free dating app and social network for singles; the perfect place to meet new people, in an instant. Whether you want to find friends, make genuine matches, find meaningful connections, chat with strangers, make new friends, or even expand your professional and social network, we’ve got you covered.

Changing the rules of dating

Bumble is a free dating app (to download and use) founded on respect, equality, and inclusion. You can find dates, meet up, and meet new people the way you've always done — but on Bumble, women always make the first move. You won’t find that on any other dating apps. 🕒 With heterosexual matches, women have 24h to start a chat, and men have 24h to respond 💬 Other matches (LGBTQIA+) have 24h to start a chat or reply before the match expires 👥 Bumble comes in 3 modes to suit what you're looking for: Date, BFF, and Bizz

Discover our amazing features

Meet new people, make new friends, or find a great date using our free dating app. We’ve levelled up from the days of dating sites, and now you have all these features at your fingertips: 👉 Unlimited Swipe: Meet new people by swiping left and right as much as you like 💬 Unlimited chat so you can find the right matches 🎵 Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends 📹 Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better

Match with the right people

We're the first app to combine dating for singles, meeting new people, and making professional connections all in one app. We’re different from other dating apps, because we make it easy for you to connect. 📹Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better 📷 Send your videos and favorite pictures while you are chatting with new friends 💤 With Snooze Mode, hide your profile whenever you want (you'll still keep all your matches!) 🎵 Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends

Boost your dating life with Bumble Premium

Bumble is a free dating app to download and use, and always will be! Our Premium features help you enhance your Bumble experience. 💛 See everyone who swiped right on you (your Beeline) 🔁 Rematch with expired connections for a second chance at a date 🔄 Extend your matches by 24 hours The buzz is real Bumble is much more than just a dating app for singles, or your average speed dating night. Join our like-minded dating community, meet new people, find your ideal partner or date. Here are our core values: 💛 We believe healthy relationships are fundamental to living a productive and positive life 💛 In the fight against old-fashioned hetero-norms, women always take the first step. 💛We've changed the rules of the game to switch up the dynamics of dating 💛Unlike other dating apps, kindness is at the core of everything we do Inclusivity is key We’re committed to being totally inclusive, and supportive of our community whatever their gender, sexual orientation, or religion. Whether you’re looking for a place to find friends, a gay dating app, a bisexual dating app, a lesbian dating app, an LGBTQ dating app, a Christian dating app or a Jewish dating app; We’ve got everything you’re looking for in our lovely community. --- Bumble is a dating app that is free to download and use. We also offer optional subscription packages (Bumble Boost and Bumble Premium) and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features (Bumble Spotlight and Bumble SuperSwipe). Your personal data is securely stored on Bumble - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions https://bumble.com/en/privacy https://bumble.com/en/terms Bumble Inc. is the parent company of Bumble, along with the dating apps Badoo and Fruitz. Enjoy all our dating apps!
summary: The dating app to meet new people, chat and date with singles or make friends!

comments: ["It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "I have emailed support multiple times about transferring my premium subscription from a previously deleted account to my new account and there has been absolutely no response from anyone in support. Unlike other dating apps that allow you to re-instate previously purchased subscriptions without having to email support (that doesn't respond to you anyway), Bumble just really need to sort its issues out.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', 'Bait and switched into "subscription". If I wanted to continue after the 1 month trial I agreed to paid for, I would have chosen a less expensive package. I cancelled the subscription and contacted support 20 minutes after charged, I had to open a PayPal case. 2 weeks later Bumble hasnt responsed. Bait and switch auto-subscriptions are theft. Ive lost $60 to this "free" app and have zero dates to show for it, just "content sellers" posting their Instagram and onlyfans.', 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "So there is a subscription model for 21 dollars a month, but this subscription does not come with the ability to see who likes you. For that, you'd need ANOTHER subscription 13 dollars more expensive than the regular subscription. To unlock seeing who likes you, you have to pay 35 bucks a month. That's gotta be an accident, right? Why would this feature not be in the regular subscription?", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", 'I tried several times to get my picture verified, including taking a picture, posting it, and then without moving, taking the same picture in the verify area. They still said I could not be verified. I contacted customer service about it, and my app got stuck on the verify photo page and would not leave that page. I then contacted customer service two more times about it and still stuck. It would be nice to at least be able to try the app out.', "Well developed but core functionality is behind a paywall, and there's no incentive to pay for an app that feels dead. Honestly it looks great but actually seeing who has matched you is behind a pricy paywall, so it's a dice roll as to whether two people see each other, and this makes the limited ability to like people (an otherwise good feature) greatly lower the ceiling on chances of matching. People have moved onto other apps.", 'The app needs work on how it recognizes and interacts with phone media. It\'s difficult to get it to recognize videos & it has double standards when it comes to photos and videos. The app allows the most pixelated pictures you\'ll ever see; however, it won\'t let me upload perfectly fine videos due to "low quality" (they\'re not), wrong dimensions (huh?), or not being shot on my phone (really?). So far, it\'s not very user-friendly.', "Swear this app is a con. I have 9 so say 'matches waiting for me'. I just used a boost and spent the full 30 minutes swiping to see if I would get anywhere with any of them (get rid of or properly match with them) and I didn't come across a single one of these people. It is so blatantly a scam just to make people feel like they have no option but to pay to see more etc etc...", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Bought premium (little under $9/wk because it was on sale). Was good at first but right now it's not letting me view profiles of people who have liked me (I can see their picture but when I click on them a blank square comes up instead of their profile). Literally the only reason I bought premium was so I could see people who liked me, so it's very frustrating that the feature stopped working. Hopefully it will work again soon. Edit: also not letting me send or view messages right now. :/", 'Very good idea but poor efficiency; is a pity that girls have only 24 hrs to establish a contact... Also, you should put more filters: for example: eyes color, hair color, etc., and stablish options to search by that criteria; for exemple, if I only want to meet people without kids or blonde girls or short (or tall) girls, be able to find those persons easily.', "The premium option is nice, maybe a little expensive for what you get. My issue is that with the premium subscription you run out of people within your filters. But if you're subscription ends you will run out of likes before you run out of people within your filters. Things don't add up properly.", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides.", "Don't recommend, I submitted seven verification photos exactly the way my profile poster was & when I tried to get customer support I've gotten zero response back other than them saying they verified who I am but to try to keep verifying my picture that matches. I paid for the week premium & the app is still stuck in the verification process & will not let me move forward. & they're still trying to charge me of subscription fee. The email I get back from customer service is a auto generated", "Horrible experience - they aren't responding to my emails to restore my lifetime premium membership. Been writing to them since two weeks to restore the unlimited premium subscription that I bought previously, no response to whatsoever, just an auto reply that we've received your email. The worst customer team ever. I don't even know if they'll fix this for me, but I'll continue to follow up."]

★Challenge: Fight on the street to earn the ranks. You have No.1 dogs.Bravo!

['A buggy mess. It logged me into someome elses account, and wouldnt register any gold i picked up, so the dog i apparently now own will forever be sick and hungry. Jarringly weird would be a way to describe it, and thats without even going into the empty microtransactions Hell that is this game. Definitely not worth even trying, its that busted.', "Installed the game, it took me to someone's account. I tried to log out and get my own account but I'm legit stuck in this account the game will not delete the account info from my phone.", "This game looks adorable and I'd love to play it but I can't. It crashes anytime you try to open the app", "I can't even do the app. It's just A gray screen. I do not recommend playing.", "This is the first time downloading the game and when I hit start to start the game, it loads someone else's account that is named Hannah! I am not playing this game that someone else purchased!", 'I love it would like more clothes and more toys like pull ropes and tennis balls for in the house and maybe if we can feed them of wifi', 'Couldnt even open the app. Crashed every time.', "It's good but when I installed it, it logined me into someone's account. Please fix this.", 'Game kept crashing before I could even start.', 'The game wont let me report a user whose been asking me inappropriate questions and at one point had an inappropriate picture. Could you please fix the report button?', 'Unable to play because crashes', 'I love the game but we res cat sweetie I miss it', "My account get hacked? Didn't login for few months, now I open it and my account became others. My dog disappeared. What happen", "I'm not sure if this is related to the game My Dog??? Or is it a direct copy? Please advise! One star for now-", 'I DONT GET WHY PEOPLE RATE THIS SO LOW!!!!! THIS GAME IS AMAZING + MY DOG WAS A COPY OF THIS BELIVE IT OR NOT. YA, THIS IS THE ORIGINAL MY DOG GAME BRO', "sucks, won't even load..", 'My dog is find but she is very good when i call her she run to me😍😘', "I'm love animals game", "Why the heck am I on someone else's account?? Fix this!", 'Logged me in someone elses game', 'What happened to dog sweetie and friends', 'I DONT LIKE IT', "It takes me to someone else's account.", "It won't let me play anymore it says I need to update it but I just downloaded it AnD tried to log back in", '作为一个小学生，第一次接触的手机游戏就是心动小狗，玩了两年，然后玩我的世界去了，下载回来的时候发现游戏名不一样了，更多的东西要钱了。不过为了回忆，我就不打算删除了。', "This game is really cute and fun but it has a lot of problems connecting to 
the WIFI, and I don't know why but it never let's me put my own profile pic 
in it. Please fix these two Problems then I'll think about giving 5 stars 
😕😦", 'I love this game and all the cute breeds but I wish I knew how to get diamonds without having to buy them but all in all I love this game.', 'So I would like to speak to one of your workers because I think I was 
hacked on my game 3 minutes ago', 'Ooh I love this game so much because whoever made this game is SUPER good 
at it...love dogs play this game...', 'I really enjoy this game it helps me get ready for me to have a real dog and its really fun it has all the different types of dogs its unbelievable', 'I like this game you can mate on it', 'I loved it because I love taking care of dogs!!!🐕🐕🐕', 'The best', 'I wish it would delete in it', "I think this is a very great game. You can have a variety of dogs and you can talk to people, and it's just very fun. The two reasons I have a 4 star rating is beacue 1. It's super hard to get diamonds. 2. Almost EVERYONE on the game is Chinese, and I know it's a Chinese game, but I can't talk to anyone. Iwouls like for more English people to play so I have people to talk to. Also, it's should not be that hard to get diamonds. Please considerthe diamond change and let's all have a fun time together. If you would like me as a friend on DogSweetie, my name is AussieBoss.", "Dogs Sweetie is my favorite game that involves taking care of dogs and them able to have puppies. The graphics are really cute and realistic. [The puppy's howl I'd super cute.] After I got a new phone and I wanted to get a game that includes dogs and puppies and this was my second choice. Although my first choice, I realised, was less developed than this game, so I went with Dogs Sweetie and I didn't regret it. They helped me recover my account from some time ago. Though I must say, this game does require a lot in order for your dog to have puppies, requiring the intimacy and 12 skills, which in order to learn a skill, your dog needs to become fully mature, will take quite some time.", "I love this game and dogs but can you add an update to this I really want my dogs back and I lost my account an update what I'm thinking was to use ur code to enter your account I would really want that so please update this", 'I love the game 🐕🐕🐕🐩🐩🐩🐕🐕🐕', 'Cute little dogs', 'Fun&cute']

title: Dog Scanner: Breed Recognition
description: The Dog Scanner app will identify your dog's breed reliably in just a few seconds! Besides taking a picture, you can also record a video or upload an image from your gallery. Got a mixed breed? No problem, the Dog Scanner app also recognizes mixed breeds! We provide you with detailed data and interesting facts about the different breeds of your mixed breed dog. No dog around? Doesn’t matter! The Dog Scanner app also recognizes humans: Simply scan yourself, your friends, your family or the people around you and find out which dogs you resemble the most! ------ NEW! Become a part of our Dog Scanner community! Share your results and compare them to the results of the community! Upload pictures of your favorite dog to our Social Feed and share them with other dog lovers! Have a look at the profiles and photos of other users, like and comment on posts from our dog community and filter them by date or popularity! Additionally, you can easily share your posts with your friends by simply sending a picture directly from the Dog Scanner app. ------ NEW! Catch all dog breeds and become an expert! Catch all the dog breeds with our Gamification feature – just like in Pokémon Go! Master the challenges, earn virtual treats and become a true dog expert! Compete with your friends or users from the community and climb to the top of our ranking list! ------ All dog breeds in the Dog Scanner app! The Dog Scanner app currently identifies more than 370 different dog breeds, including all breeds officially recognized by the Fédération Cynologique Internationale (FCI) and even some more! Our comprehensive database with information and pictures of all dog breeds (including the unofficial ones) can also be accessed completely without scanning! Give us feedback on the Dog Scanner app! Let us know if the dog’s breed has been correctly identified. If not, you will get useful tips to improve your own results. If you also indicate which dog breed is in the picture, you help us to enhance our software since the app automatically learns how to provide even more accurate outcomes. Also suggest or vote for (unofficial) dog breeds that you want us to add to the app in the future! Get your premium upgrade! With our premium version, the app will no longer show ads and your results will be available faster. Furthermore, you can now choose whether your dog breeds should be recognized rather quickly or with higher accuracy. With the premium version, scanning dogs is also possible in offline mode, so you no longer need an active internet connection to identify their breeds. With the optional in-app purchase of our premium version, you will also help to support this app. ------ Find us on social media! On our social media channels we provide you with the most beautiful dog pictures from the community. You will also find many interesting facts about man's best friend. Furthermore, we will keep you updated on all new added features of the Dog Scanner app in the future. * Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dogscanner_app * Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DogScannerApp * Twitter: https://twitter.com/dogscanner_app ------ Just give it a shot! Dog recognition as easy as it gets! Despite the small app size you will get all features and be able to identify a dog’s breed or get access to our extensive database at any time! Before you consider getting an expensive DNA test, simply scan your dog with the app and the dog breed will automatically be determined within seconds! Download the Dog Scanner app now!
summary: See a dog, but don't know its breed? Just take a picture and find out!
